### RabbitMQ başlat: docker run -p 5672:5672 -p 15672:15672 rabbitmq:management
### RabbitMQ UI: http://localhost:15672 (guest/guest)

### Sipariş oluştur — OrderCreatedEvent publish edilir
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
  "totalAmount": 299.99
}

### Kargo eventi gönder — OrderShippedEvent publish edilir
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders/1234/ship

### Birden fazla sipariş oluştur — consumer'ların paralel çalıştığını gör
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Mehmet Kaya",
  "totalAmount": 149.99
}

###
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Ayşe Demir",
  "totalAmount": 499.99
}